705215f-a.title: Brooklyn: Kings Highway - McDonald Avenue
705215f-a.text:
481-495 King's Highway, north side, between Mc Donald Ave., and East 2nd Street. No. 495 is in the foreground. The Culver Elevated Line
of the B.M.T. is in the background.
March 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
